00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:46.680
And in the end, the Wild West ends up
looking a lot more like industrial capitalism
than like a Larry McMurtry novel.

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:54.600
The Wild West, like the rest of the industrialized world, was incentivized to increase productivity and was shaped by an increasingly international economic system.

00:11:54.600 --> 00:11:59.560
